<step><![CDATA[
mix flour and baking powder into a bowl, make a well in the centger (3) add oil / melted lard if using (4) add starter and work into dough (5) add water and work into dough]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[
roll dough into a log 50 cm long, cut 2.5 cm pieces (7) with each piece, roll into a ball, flatten on table, then roll out in 7,5 cm disks thicker at the center (8) place filling in center and twist tops (9) steam 8 m or so
